Package: biorxiv
Type: Package
Title: Search and Download Papers from the biorxiv.org Preprint Server
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2015-01-20
Author: Edmund Hart <edmund.m.hart@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Edmund Hart <edmund.m.hart@gmail.com>
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Description: The biorxiv preprint server (http://www.biorxiv.org) is a website where scientists can post preprints of biology.  It hosts raw text abstracts and pdf's of these papers. Users can search and download PDF's in bulk for text mining or other purposes. The text of abstracts is stored as raw text within R, and PDF's can easily be imported for textmining with packages like tm.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    XML
VignetteBuilder: knitr
